Startpage Is Upset About My VPN
text: I started using startpage on account of someone mentioning it here on HN, and I rarely find that I need to go through Google directly for a search query. Unfortunately though, I keep getting these captchas because it doesn't recognize me through my VPN. It isn't a huge issue, but it's pretty inconvenient when, for example, it's 1 AM on Saturday night/Sunday morning.  Is there an easy solution for that or can complain loudly enough here that the interface gets improved?
